    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed your <strong>peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut them into thick strips</p><p>Peel and roughly slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> and<strong> sliced onion</strong> to a separate baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20 min or until the veg is soft and tender – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1707825293483-x200.jpg",
