            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1707825305829-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until the chicken is slightly blackened on the outside and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>smoky Spanish-style chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1707825309707-x200.jpg",
