            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1707825313508-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky Spanish-style free range chicken</strong> with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong> and <strong>roasted veg </strong>to the side</p><p>Top the crispy potatoes with the <strong>bravas sauce</strong> – these are your <strong>patatas bravas</strong></p><p>Drizzle the<strong> aioli</strong> all over the patatas bravas</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
